<br>
Wife (mage) and I were in Sol A for quite a while and pets never took agro for more than two hits or so even if I skipped on the dots and such.  Any time I got within striking distance the mobs were MINE.  Striking distance here is absurd too so when in a smaller room I couldnt sit to med either.  Seems like mobs here have giant distance melee (not really but seems like it).<br>
