After wife made it to 29 and got new spells we moved to the tizmaks in GD.  As long as I dont get crazy with dot's right away I won't have agro at all during the fight for the most part.<br>
<br>
Sooooo.........I am thinking it may have something to do with being outdoors as opposed to indoors, or it may have been that the pets were too far apart in levels to hold the agro on thier own (I was using 30 pet buff, wife had her 24 spell while in sol a, 29 in GD)<br>
<br>
Maybe the peeps not holding agro could post what zones and levels of pets, might help clear things up a bit.<br>
